# Claude Code statusline config
# Copy to ~/.claude/statusline.conf, then chmod 600.

# ─── Plan tier (only used as fallback if scrape fails) ───────────────
# pro    — $20/mo  — 5h~$8,   7d~$50
# max5   — $100/mo — 5h~$40,  7d~$280
# max20  — $200/mo — 5h~$160, 7d~$1120
CC_PLAN=max5

# ─── sessionKey FALLBACK (usually leave empty) ───────────────────────
# fetch-real-usage.sh reads live from Chromium browser cookie DB by default
# (auto-rotates as Anthropic refreshes the cookie). Only set this if NO
# Chromium browser is installed or cookie DB is inaccessible.
#
# How to get one: claude.ai → F12 → Application → Cookies → sessionKey value
SESSION_KEY=""

# ─── Org UUID (auto-detected from lastActiveOrg cookie) ──────────────
# Override only if you have multiple orgs and the active-org detection picks wrong.
# Find via: curl -s -H "Authorization: Bearer <oauth>" \
#           https://api.anthropic.com/api/oauth/profile | jq .organization.uuid
ORG_UUID=""
